  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a Phase 1 Open-Label, Parallel-Group, Single-Dose Study to evaluate the
      Pharmacokinetics of GS-5816 in subjects with normal hepatic function and moderate or severe
      hepatic impairment.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
